palm er , ala ska providence matanuska health_care has an immediate opportunity for an experienced mental_health nurse practitioner to join our out_patient clinic . we provide psychiatric diagnostic interviews , medication management , neuropsychological / psychological testing , individual / family / couples / group therapy and neurofeedback in an out_patient setting . excellent compensation and generous benefits_package , plus unparalleled quality of life in beautiful ala ska . providence matanuska health_care provides full_spectrum care for all people of all ages . the clinic is located in the scenic matanuska-susitna valley 40 miles from anchorage , where providence operates the state s largest and most comprehensive medi_cal center and its only children s hospital . our team of family medicine and pediatric physicians includes dr . cathy baldwin-johnson , founder of the practice , who was nationally recognized as the national family practice physician of the year in 2002 . ala ska offers financial , cultural and recreational opportunities beyond compare . there is no state income or sales tax ; in fact the state pays every alaska n a yearly dividend from oil revenues !
